name: Myasiatrade
tag_list: asia-shoppping, china-wholesale-e-commerce, china-marketplace, online-shopping, discount-shopping, group-buying, asia-affiliate-marketing, china-affiliate-marketing
overview:
Myasiatrade.com is an online shopping site, offering items at discount price without minimum order. Affiliate and reseller programs are available and its free to join.

Myasiatrade.com provides discount shopping on almost any categories, from electronics to wedding, from fashion to jewelry. Myasiatrade.com is not a marketplace, rather its a store by itself. Easy to use, you are dealing with 1 seller and its not dealing with thousand different sellers. 1 simple customer service center to deal with if you ever have any problem.
